They use a straightforward approach based on the well-known principle of vaccination – vaccinate with what you want to develop protection against. The significant possibilities of such vaccines have been described, but none have yet passed the clinical trial stage. Antigenic essence technology is the revitalization of cellular vaccination, as antigenic essence exhibits all the identifying properties of cancer cells while also allowing for control of composition, purification from ballast substances (cellular 'noise'), and evasion of MHC restrictions. Our antigenic essence technology platform is behind the development of the potential candidates for cancer vaccine, under the brand name SANTAVAC, that can be tuned against virtually any solid cancer. We are located in Keller / Fort Worth, Texas and see clients in person at our office at 9500 Ray White Rd, Suite 200, Fort Worth, TX 76244 as well as through online counseling. Marriage Counseling / Marriage Therapy - Keller / Fort WorthMarriage Counseling is for married or unmarried couples who are seeking to improve their relationship by improving communication, coping skills, understanding of one another, and the time that they put into their relationship. Marriage Counseling has been shown to decrease rates of divorce and improve quality of life for families. Our Therapists see clients every week who were on the verge of separation or divorce who have now decided to try to improve their relationship in order to stay together. Teen Counseling / Teen Therapy - Keller / Fort WorthTeens are experiencing a time like never before. With concerns regarding school, grades, peer pressures, work stress, as well as social media and the impact of everything being so public nowadays, teens are under tremendous pressure to perform. In recent years, we have seen increases in teen/adolescent suicide, cutting, teenage pregnancy, and many other factors. We at LBCC promise to come alongside your teen and you as the parent, ensuring that open lines of communication are created as well as plans to improve behavior, emotional struggles, and overall relationship functioning. Anxiety / Depression Therapy - Keller / Fort WorthThere have been rises in adults and teens suffering from anxiety, stress, and depression related struggles in recent years. Anxiety and Depression counseling is aimed at meeting clients where they are emotionally, then helping the client to find within themselves the tools and skills to improve their mental health wellbeing.

Description: Scales & Tails Exotic Pets is a family owned and operated online pet and pet supply business.
Full Description: My name is Sky, and I, along with my wife and my crazy son, started Scales & Tails Exotic Pets. We are a family owned and operated online pet and pet supply company.   As a young kid I LOVED to go to the local pet stores. For me they were always the ultimate fun spot. The puppies and kittens were always cool and fun to play with but my real interest came from the excitement and sense of wonder that came from the other animals. You know, the ones found in the darker rooms that were always pushed to the back of the stores.  These were the rooms that housed the lizards, snakes, fish, and other "exotic" small animals that always seemed so mysterious to me.  I was hooked before I even owned my first reptile. I can tell you a whole story about how after owning lots of different animals I realized that good quality products at decent prices are super hard to find, blah blah blah, but I won't.  We all know the reality is that good quality products are easy to find. The truth is that I have always wanted to own my own pet and pet supply store.  I LOVE working with animals, I LOVE working with people (as long as your nice, I don't really like the not nice people).  I love learning from and teaching others.  I have made lots of mistakes in my adventures of animal husbandry, and I know that I'll make more.  If I can help one other person avoid the same mistakes I've made and end up with a happy, healthy animal then I've accomplished my goal. With over 20 years experience keeping reptiles, amphibians, and fish we've learned a lot. One thing we absolutely know is that there is a lot we don't know. Our promise to you is that if we don't know the answer to a question we won't make it up. We will happily tell you we don't know, and then we will help you find the answer from credible and reliable sources. We're here for YOU.  Ask us questions, talk to us about your dream setups, tell us how weird your friends think you are for keeping a bunch of frozen rats in your freezer next to the ice cream. We'd love to hear from you!

Headquarters Location: New York, New York, United States
Description: Investment information and trends revealed through mining financial regulatory filings
Full Description: Financial services industries including asset management, capital markets, and insurance are regulated. As a result, firms in these industries make several filings with their regulators. These filings reveal invaluable information but the data is hard to use. We structure, enrich, and analyze this data to make it actionable. Currently RADiENT acquires data from filings made by asset managers with the SEC. These filings have a depth of information about these firm, their investments, and their customers. In the aggregate this information is a powerful tool to monitor industry trends including fund flows and service provider activity. We structure, scrub, and normalize this data for analysis using machine learning and natural language processing tools. We then enrich it with information we gather from other public sources such as the news, social media, and related market data. Key use cases: -Investment manager due diligence and ongoing monitoring for investors -Asset management research for consulting firms and financial institutions -Sales prospecting e.g. which financial advisers should a fund complex targeting investment advisers, or a brokerage firm targeting hedge funds -Generating investment ideas e.g. using portfolio disclosures and indications of large holders or insider sales We automatically source, extract, and structure information from government regulatory filings websites run by agencies such as the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC), Commodity Futures Trading Commission (CFTC), Federal Reserve, and Department of Labor (DOL). In addition, we enrich this data from public sources including FINRA's Broker Check website, other public industry websites, news, and social media. Lastly, we acquire and structure market prices and other data on market indices, investment funds and securities from a diverse set of financial data sources such as financial websites, fund complex websites, fund factsheet documents and investor presentations. Enabling performance charting and risk analysis of securities that are impacted by these regulatory filings including the tracking of complete portfolios of securities.
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US

Description: Affordable Premium Delivery Services
Full Description: C2C Delivery, registered in Delaware, is a pioneering platform in the grocery delivery sector, challenging the status quo established by Instacart. With an unwavering commitment to fairness and transparency, C2C Delivery is redefining how consumers and shoppers engage in the grocery delivery space. Key Features: * No Markups: C2C Delivery ensures that customers pay the same prices as they would in-store, eliminating the extra costs often associated with Instacart. * Transparent Pricing: Every delivery includes the original store receipt, offering customers a clear and honest breakdown of their spending. * Customizable Shopper Selection: Customers have the freedom to choose their shoppers by browsing through various shopper profiles and delivery bids, ensuring a personalized and satisfactory service. * Competitive and Fair Delivery Fees: The platform's unique bidding system for delivery orders fosters a competitive environment, resulting in fair and reasonable delivery fees. * Incentivized Shoppers: By directing the entirety of delivery fees and tips to the shoppers, C2C Delivery motivates the shoppers to consistently deliver top-notch service. * Flexible Delivery Options: The service caters to a range of needs, from urgent one-hour deliveries to convenient pick-up options. * Straightforward Membership Structure: Offering a transparent membership fee structure comparable to Instacart, C2C Delivery also provides a simple flat usage fee for non-members per order. Vision: C2C Delivery's mission is to transform the grocery delivery landscape by prioritizing transparency, fairness, and customer choice. We strive to build a community where hidden costs are a thing of the past, and every transaction is clear, fair, and customer-centric.  Join us on our journey to create a unique and trust-based grocery delivery experience, distinctly different from traditional models.

It uses neural network technology.  · Manni Upsell is a small box with microphones that is placed where people check out in stores. It listens to employees, recognizes what they are saying, and measures their sales ability. This includes how often they are offering customers the option to purchase an additional item- an “upsale”. Each product uses facial and/or voice recognition to identify which employee is working at the time. This lets managers cross reference sales ability and customer satisfaction to specific employees. Each product includes two parts: the “devices” that are physically in the client’s store and an online interface that lets managers look at the generated data.
